When reporting any bugs, please don't forget to include a detailed
description of the bug and tell me, if it is reproduceable or not.
Please also mention the version number of DRAFU you used and describe
your system configuration (Amiga model 500/.../4000T-060, Kickstart/OS,
RAM, HardDisk, special configurations).

If you want to get a newer - and maybe debugged - version of DRAFU
do not forget to register as an user of DRAFU with the included
registration form.
Nevertheless unregistered users are as welcome to report bugs as
users who decide(d) to register.


